Introduction

My name is Charles Ross and Im a GIS Analyst, Data Visualization Specialist, Data Engineer and Data Scientist who specializes in using programs such as ArcGIS, R Shiny, Power BI, and Tableau to create interactive and dynamic dashboards, maps, reports, graphs, tables, and other applications that meets the request of my clients who are either looking for new features to add to an existing platform, or are looking for a new tool to explore information within their own organization. I also specialize in utilizing various coding languages such as Python, R, and SQL to clean and analyze large datasets, streamline data processing workflows, as well as maintain and organize databases.
This page is a portfolio of past project I have completed for clients, achievements I have accomplished throughout my career, and of the personal projects I pursue in my spare time. Please feel free to explore these dashboards, graphs, tables, reports and applications at your leisure, and if you have any questions, please feel free to send me a message, my contact information can be found at the bottom of this page.
